Fortis Healthcare Falls After Founder Pledges 204 Million Shares

-- B y   N i v e d i t h a   R a v i
-- 
2011-09-16T09:35:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/fortis-healthcare-falls-after-founder-pledges-204-million-shares.html
Fortis Healthcare India Ltd. fell
as much as 4 percent after its founder has pledged 54 million
more shares.  The shares fell 2.2 percent to 147.25 as of 3.02 p.m. local
time. Fortis Healthcare Holdings Ltd. has pledged a total of 204
million shares, or 50.4 percent of equity, according to an
exchange filing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Niveditha Ravi at 
 nravi2@bloomberg.net  